{"tid":2196981,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"90後(95或之前), 很快我們30了 ...","createTime":"2020-09-10T09:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T11:45:52.000Z","uid":272077,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a86392a251db7f3dbc174c53f923e4c12cb05649","tid":2196981,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"不知不覺就30了, 當天大學/大專, 中學時, 小學時的記憶和生活情境還瀝瀝在目, 就像昨天的事一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不知為何, 天天上班, 沒有什麼好值得記憶下的, 上班下班上班下班, 這樣又一天了, 這樣又一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你的工作有什麼回憶呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天剛和朋友談起往事, 不知不覺, 我們老了, 時間過得很快.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就到30的你, 人生目標完成了多少? 你的人生又沒有後悔呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油呀, 明天依然是我們的, 明天依然是充滿希望的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a809a656868d63c56c98bae0fdf31fd7a774122","tid":2196981,"uid":369035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩又收到喜帖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}